		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Loading from disc takes about 7 seconds, no matter how many data you load.
<br />The disk drive lacks any kind of tracking motor which enable fast acess to any location on the disc.
<br />The BIOS either copy data to/from drive, or ignores the data.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
